						 <p>If say, someone like the Chaos insurgency got a hold of SCP-1318, imagine the Conversations<br /> &quot;Say what shall we do tonight Frankie?&quot;<br /> &quot;Same thing we do every night, Try to take over the world!&quot;</p> 
