					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-473848#post-2747055</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-473848/scp-1318#post-2747055</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 14 Feb 2017 15:12:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DrFred</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1377450</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Ok, am I the only one CONVINCED that Frankie really is that smart, but he can only communicate telepathically (tiny vocal chords) be making the other person sub-vocalize?</p> <p>He is giving them info they did not consciously have before. That seems like Frankie si an entity.</p> <p>I guess this could be tested by asking him about old help he had already given, while the expert on that old topic is out of the room?</p> <p>The idea of wanting more of him seems logical, as does the idea that you shouldn't waste time working inefficiently when efficiant work options are available?</p> <p>+1</p> <p>Also, there is a chance I have already been affected.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
